\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9258539 TJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14097773\charrsid13784614 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13981439 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14097773\charrsid13784614 Did your parents go to church at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9258539 TJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14097773\charrsid13784614 No. No. Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13981439 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14097773\charrsid13784614 Do you know what denomination they would have called themselves? Were they Catholic or Church of England?
