 - no, I could never remember my mother or father - speaking of - in regards to religion what - church of England or Catholics, never, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13981439 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14097773\charrsid13784614 Would you have considered yourself anything at that time?
