\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9258539 TJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14097773\charrsid13784614 Well they lived in a pub.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13981439 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14097773\charrsid13784614 Did they have any other leisure activities, did they do anything else at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9258539 TJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14097773\charrsid13784614 
Oh - my father was a big gambler, as I've told you before, he named me after a racehorse, Tommy Tittlemouse. He back that horse. He won it and - I was born at the same time so he said, we'll have him - so my mother says, we'll have him Thomas, 
as I backed Tommy Tittlemouse so we'll back him - we'll name him Thomas. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13981439 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14097773\charrsid13784614 Can you remember as a child what would happen if your father had a big win on anything?
