 - quite proud carrying a whip being a bad boy. He said, how old are you? I said, fourteen sir. All right, run over and get your birth certificate. I went home, my mother happened to be in that morning. She said, what do you want, aren't you going to work
? I says, he wants me birth certificate. So she said, oh that's had it she said - she said, you're not fourteen yet. Oh she did swear and all. Oh she was a proper ruffian.
