,
 I don't know whether it's silver or gold but - it must have been of value because when I got home my mum said, what did they give you? As usual. I said, look, give us a lovely medal. She said - I remember her saying, oh that's nice isn't it, that's very 
nice. So she said, put it on the mantelpiece. I put on the ma}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3631160\charrsid13784614 n}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14097773\charrsid13784614 tel}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
